  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599940284804-C6VNPGQS8QFYY5CIYTZO/18a-preggers-428x600.jpg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n<p>photo by <a href=\"http://www.danacolwell.com/index2.php\">Dana Colwell</a> Yes, it's true - time is flying by quickly. We found out the sex of the baby a few weeks ago but thought we would share it here since so many of you have asked. A couple hours after finding out the news, I came home and got excited about documenting it for Project Life, so I whipped up a journaling card. I used part of a <a href=\"http://www.studiocalico.com/waiting-list/project-life?aff=6cc2c70f\">Project Life kit by Studio Calico</a> and some <a href=\"http://www.shareasale.com/r.cfm?u=530666&amp;b=199868&amp;m=24698&amp;afftrack=tim%20holtz&amp;urllink=www%2Esimonsaysstamp%2Ecom%2Fservlet%2Fthe%2DRanger%2DTim%2DHoltz%2DDistress%2DPaints%2FCategories\">Tim Holtz Distress Paint</a> as the base.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"18b-DSC_0969-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599940315204-G8XM67F12M3Z5NCJWIF9/18b-DSC_0969-600x398.jpg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"18c-DSC_0970-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599940315282-94IW0ENC8LX2SSWZ2KR4/18c-DSC_0970-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"18d-DSC_0972-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599940315530-7BHV71BKLAWS7NB8XSF9/18d-DSC_0972-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"18e-DSC_0973-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599940316018-XHMYNG77PDIRVGTVV91X/18e-DSC_0973-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"18f-DSC_0974-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599940316347-MUD6SF1772OSZMSLET6D/18f-DSC_0974-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>I adhered some <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/freckled-fawn/135939-wide-aqua-chevron-washi-tape/%3Ffilters%3Dfreckled-fawn\">Freckled Fawn washi tape</a> along with a journaling card from <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/elles-studio/%3Fpp%3D300\">Elle's Studio</a>. And topped it off with <a href=\"http://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10513&amp;pw=41735&amp;url=http%3A//www.twopeasinabucket.com/shop/american-crafts/131573-white-everyday-printed-chipboard-ready-set-go-thicker-stickers/%3Ffilters%3D_ready_set%2Bgo_\">these Thickers</a>. The permanent marker is from this amazing <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B000OZMSYC/ref=as_li_ss_tl?ie=UTF8&amp;camp=1789&amp;creative=390957&amp;creativeASIN=B000OZMSYC&amp;linkCode=as2&amp;tag=wwwamytangeri-20\">BIC Mark-It set</a> (the colors are delightful).</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"18g-DSC_0975-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599940389577-FUOHJHP5XPHAIDSO98C3/18g-DSC_0975-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"18h-DSC_0977-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599940389582-EB4YX8RK6SBPWH8ZI6B5/18h-DSC_0977-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"18i-DSC_0979-600x398.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599940360494-E9XK7WK3QEKAGVFKXK3A/18i-DSC_0979-600x398.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"18j-DSC_0980-600x395.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1599940360560-56PZ11I448FJ7LH683YE/18j-DSC_0980-600x395.jpg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>We're delighted about the news that he's healthy, and that we get to call him a \"he\"! Is it wrong for wanting to put the ultrasound photo with the little arrow pointing to the you-know-what right next to this card? I've had Bon Jovi's song, <a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lDK9QqIzhwk\">Livin' On A Prayer</a> stuck in my head the entire time I have been composing this post. But the words ring true: Oh Baby, we're halfway there.... WHOA-OH!</p>"
}